                "tool_use_id": "tooluse_onpzIa1J4nE34kgKJ7TWXI",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "Text": "=== Operation 1 Result (Text) ===\n#!/bin/zsh\n# ─── Homebrew ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\neval \"$(/opt/homebrew/bin/brew shellenv)\"\n\n# ─── Zsh plugins (via Homebrew) ──────────────────────────────────────\nFPATH=$(brew --prefix)/share/zsh-completions:$FPATH\nautoload -Uz compinit && compinit -u\nsource $(brew --prefix)/share/zsh-autosuggestions/zsh-autosuggestions.zsh\nsource $(brew --prefix)/share/zsh-syntax-highlighting/zsh-syntax-highlighting.zsh\n\n# ─── History ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nHISTSIZE=50000\nSAVEHIST=50000\nHISTFILE=~/.zsh_history\nsetopt EXTENDED_HISTORY HIST_EXPIRE_DUPS_FIRST HIST_IGNORE_DUPS HIST_IGNORE_SPACE SHARE_HISTORY\n\n# ─── Starship prompt ────────────────────────────────────────────────\neval \"$(starship init zsh)\"\n\n# ─── fzf ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nsource <(fzf --zsh)\n\n# ─── Zoxide (smart cd) ──────────────────────────────────────────────\neval \"$(zoxide init zsh)\"\n\n# ─── Aliases ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nalias ls='lsd'\nalias ll='lsd -la'\nalias lt='lsd --tree'\nalias cd='z'\nalias cat='bat'\nalias abc='q'\n\n# ─── Proxy helper ───────────────────────────────────────────────────\nproxy () {\n    export HTTP_PROXY=http://127.0.0.1:10808\n    export HTTPS_PROXY=http://127.0.0.1:10808\n    export ALL_PROXY=socks5://127.0.0.1:10808\n    \"$@\"\n    unset HTTP_PROXY HTTPS_PROXY ALL_PROXY\n}\n\n# ─── Extra PATH ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nexport PATH=\"/opt/homebrew/opt/mysql-client/bin:$HOME/.local/bin:$PATH\"\n\n=== Operation 2 Result (Text) ===\ntheme = green-eye-care\nfont-family = MesloLGS Nerd Font\nfont-size = 14\n\n# 快速终端 (Cmd+` 呼出/隐藏)\nkeybind = global:cmd+grave_accent=toggle_quick_terminal\n\n# 滚动缓冲区加大，方便看长日志\nscrollback-limit = 100000\n\n# 光标样式\ncursor-style = block\n\n# 窗口\nwindow-padding-x = 4\nwindow-padding-y = 4\nwindow-save-state = always\n\n# 关闭 tab/窗口时不再提示确认\nconfirm-close-surface = false\n\n#选中文字自动复制\ncopy-on-select = clipboard\n\nnotify-on-command-finish = unfocused\nnotify-on-command-finish-action = bell\n\nclipboard-read = allow\nclipboard-write = allow"
